trans-unit.source: Represents the items host for a <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonQuickAccessToolBar"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: 항목에 대 한 호스트를 나타냅니다는 <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonQuickAccessToolBar"> </xref> 개체입니다.

trans-unit.source: This class is used by <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonQuickAccessToolBar> and is not intended to be used independently.
trans-unit.target: 이 클래스는 사용 하 여 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonQuickAccessToolBar>하며 독립적으로 사용할 수 없습니다.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonQuickAccessToolBar>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Primitives.RibbonQuickAccessToolBarPanel"></xref> class.
Positions and sizes the child elements in this <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Primitives.RibbonQuickAccessToolBarPanel"></xref>.
The size that the <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Primitives.RibbonQuickAccessToolBarPanel"></xref> needs to position its child elements.
trans-unit.target: 크기는는 <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Primitives.RibbonQuickAccessToolBarPanel"> </xref> 해당 자식 요소를 배치 해야 합니다.

trans-unit.source: Measures the child elements in this <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Primitives.RibbonQuickAccessToolBarPanel"></xref> in preparation of arranging them during the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Primitives.RibbonQuickAccessToolBarPanel.ArrangeOverride*> pass.
trans-unit.target: 이 자식 요소를 측정 <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Primitives.RibbonQuickAccessToolBarPanel"> </xref> <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Primitives.RibbonQuickAccessToolBarPanel.ArrangeOverride*>통과</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Primitives.RibbonQuickAccessToolBarPanel.ArrangeOverride*> 하는 동안 정렬 하기 위한 준비

trans-unit.source: Called when the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.Items%2A?displayProperty=fullName> collection of the <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl"></xref> associated with this object changes.
trans-unit.target: 될 때 호출의 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.Items%2A?displayProperty=fullName> 의 컬렉션은 <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl"> </xref> 연결 된이 개체 변경 합니다.
